reviews.review_text: My first show This was the first show I went into, and, well, the rest is history. The birdsong blew my 3-hit airplane tripped mind, and I was hooked! I remember saying to my friends after they finished birdsong and left the stage for set break, "what the fuck is going on, where they going, that was the most insane thing I have ever heard!!!" They just laughed, very hard!!!
